    v1 = ((wp.cos(tmp + 0.08) - wp.cos(tmp + 0.10)) * v2)
    v0 = (v2 + ((v0 + 0.05 / v0 + 0.46) / tmp))
    v2 = (0.20 + v1)
    v1 = wp.sin((0.97 - (v1 + 0.27 + v1 + 0.08)))

    v2 = (v0 * wp.abs((v2 + 0.15 / v0 + 0.77)))
